Opentronix Development Guide
============================

The source code is hosted as a git repository at
https://github.com/Opentronix/Opentronix

Coding style
------------
Text width
~~~~~~~~~~
The text width should not exceed 80 characters. Exceptions to this should be
used only in rare cases.

Indentation
~~~~~~~~~~~
For indentation tabs are used.

Conditionals
~~~~~~~~~~~~
The opening curly brace is on the same line as the +if+, the +elseif+ or the
+else+. The closing curly brace is on a separate line. +elseif+ and +else+ are
also on a separate line.

